This torrent works fine (and its in English, and strangely the model chick gets hotter as the series goes on, she is ugly to begin with).

See notes on DVD 1 comments for how to mount it - I suggest use PowerISO personally as the easiest way, Daemontools should work too.  Otherwise you have to make a drive D: and it has to be D: - with ISO mounting it can be any drive letter.

There are a handful of us seeding these disks.  Please help or we will eventually go away and nobody will be able to download these except at a crawl.

I strongly endorse the try before you buy principle and it obviously helps keep outrageous software prices down.   I think this disk series is excellent - even if it reflects some of the ridiculous complexities Cubase itself has - and is well worth buying.   Just a note.
